import React from 'react'
import Serviceimg from '../Component/Service Component/Serviceimg'
import Servicetop from '../Component/Service Component/Servicetop'
import Otherslide from '../Component/Otherslide'
import Labstpes from '../Component/Labsteps'
import Stillimg from '../Component/Stillimg'
import Servicesteps from '../Component/Service Component/Servicesteps'
import Servicetext from '../Component/Service Component/Servicetext'



export default function Service() {
    return (
        <>

            <Otherslide />
            <Servicetop />
            <Serviceimg />
            <Labstpes />
            <Servicesteps />
            <Stillimg />
            <Servicetext />









        </>
    )
}
